Program: Discovery
Title: American Association for Advancement of Science
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrw5n
Last Broadcast Date: 21 February 1994
Special report from annual meeting of American Association for Advancement of Science. Includes lasers for sculpting atoms: the origin of life from frozen ocean: why half of the secret of life, lies outside the cell. Presented by Ruth Linton.